wikipedia_page.main: Roland D. Vickers (1896 – 21 January 1947) was an English professional golfer who played in the early 20th century. Vickers' best performance came in the 1927 Open Championship when he tied for tenth place. He finished tied for 31rd in 1933, his last appearance in the Open. In press reports he is always called "R D Vickers" but official documents do not include a middle name.
